        Gtktop installation

*** What you need ***
- OCaml 3.12 (or later) installed
- findlib
     http://projects.camlcity.org/projects/findlib.html
- Lablgtk2 >= 2.14.2 installed with findlib
     http://lablgtk.forge.ocamlcore.org/
- LablGtk-extras >= 1.1
     http://gtk-extras.forge.ocamlcore.org/
- make ;-)

*** How to compile ***
- ./configure
- make all
- make install

This will install findlib package "gtktop".